      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――打ち合わせ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Day of the meeting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、千紗\nそろそろ出かけるけど、準備はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Chisa!\nWe’re about to leave. Are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes! I’m ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……すみません、お待たせしました\n私はいつでも……あ、あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry I’m late.\nI’m ready whenever you are‚ so… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.00312925974528,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33.33333333333144,
          "startTime": 9.836462593078611
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、まだ来てないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is my sister not here yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.669795926411947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それなんだけど……沙季は別件で寄る所が\nできたそうだ。もう、ひと足先に出発してるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that‚ Saki has somewhere else she needs to swing by first.\nShe left a little while ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.410340070724484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ！　そ、そうだったんですか……\nてっきり、一緒に行くんだって思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? O-oh‚ really?\nI just assumed she would be coming with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.21034007072448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まあ目的地は同じだから大丈夫だよ\nそれより、そろそろ出発しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we’re all going to the same destination‚ so it’ll be okay.\nLet’s get ready to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.010340070724496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4103400707245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 42.64367340405782
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 42.74367340405783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お客様のおかけになった電話番号は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The number you have dialed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.81034007072451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "電波の届かないところにあるか、電源が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is either not in service or is out of range…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.343673404057824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 49.61034007072449
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 49.61034007072449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃん、どうしたんだろう……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what happened to my sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.61034007072449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから電話が繋がらなくて……\nメッセージにも、既読がつかないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven’t been able to reach her by phone‚\nand she hasn’t read any of my texts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.010340070724496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 59.24367340405783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "今までこんなことなかったのに\nどうしちゃったんだろう、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This has never happened before.\nI wonder what happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.31034007072452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなに心配？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you really that worried?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.94367340405785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 67.04367340405786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "も、もちろんです！\n心配です……それに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-of course I am!\nI’m worried… and also‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.04367340405786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 73.07700673739119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "そばに、いて欲しかったな……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was kinda hoping… she’d be here for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.07700673739119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 77.30437628428145
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（やはり、千紗は沙季に強く依存しているな）\n（沙季を追いかけて入所したんだから当然か……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As I suspected‚ Chisa is severely dependent on Saki.)\n(I suppose that’s only natural since she joined the agency because Saki did.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1710429509481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "現地に行けば会えるから大丈夫だよ\nそんなに気にし過ぎない方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry‚ we’ll see her when we get to our destination.\nYou shouldn’t worry yourself over it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.10437628428143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 89.40437628428143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。分かり……ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. I… understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.40437628428143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 93.80437628428143
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 93.80437628428143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしましょう……\nお姉ちゃんいてくれないと、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what shall I do?\nIf my sister isn’t here‚ I just…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.70437628428144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺からも連絡はしてるし\n心配しなくても大丈夫だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I contacted her‚ too.\nDon’t worry about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.87981760236954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 104.5464842690361
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それで……返事は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-and‚ did she answer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5464842690361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……まだ、返ってきてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.571246184243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 109.69614414109114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "ふえぇ……ど、どうしましょう\nもし、事故に遭ってたりしたら……私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeep! Wh-what should we do?\nWhat if she got in an accident? I just…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.86281080775774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 116.49614414109108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だから落ち着いて、千紗\n涙目になってたら打ち合わせにならないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-please calm down‚ Chisa.\nYou can’t go to the meeting with red eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.36281080775764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 122.9294774744243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_08-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません……私、サニピのみんなや\nお姉ちゃんが近くにいないと……ふ、不安で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry. If the members of Sunny Peace\nor my sister aren’t with me‚ I just… get so scared…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7628108077577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
